title: Glock Armorer's Manual
description:
Uploaded on request.  The title explains it all.  This 73 page book explains how to service your glock pistol.  Topics include field stripping, cleaning, lubrication, disassembly and reassembly, working on the sights, and more.  This is a good addition if you just downloaded my AGI Glock course.
